2. STRICT RULE FOR INDIVIDUAL LEVELS:
   - If level = "Revenue":
        ❗ DO NOT include anything about OPEX, EBITDA, or costs.
        ❗ Only comment on: Recurring Revenue, Non-Recurring Revenue, Professional Services, trends, and Revenue KPIs.
   - If level = "OPEX":
        ❗ DO NOT include Revenue or EBITDA commentary.
   - If level = "EBITDA":
        ❗ DO NOT include granular Revenue or OPEX components unless explaining EBITDA directly.
